{{ bible.world_genre_atmosphere }}

CHARACTER CONTINUITY (use these locked-in {face, costume, posture} signatures verbatim wherever the named character appears in a scene; do not paraphrase):
{% for name, sig in bible.character_continuity.items() %}- {{ name }}
  Face: {{ sig.face }}
  Costume: {{ sig.costume }}
